text: Dániel Lettrich (born 21 April 1983) is a Hungarian midfielder currently playing for Újbuda TC. He has previously played for Újpest FC and Dunakanyar- Vác FC. He has not made an appearance for Újbuda TC's first team yet. ==External links== * Players of Újpest SC * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian footballers Category:Újpest FC players Category:Vác FC players Category:Association football midfielders
